name: Womens Jayde 3/2mm Double Chest Zip Wetsuit
description:
One of our highest performing wetsuits for women, now updated with streamlined graphics. The Jayde is crafted from our top grade neoprene, Yamamoto, and lined with waterproof stretch taped seams. Combined with Flaremesh+ on the back, chest, and lower body panels, this wetsuit ensures lasting comfort and warmth, season after season.

THE DETAILS:
Waterproof stretch taping (100%): all seams
GBS (Glued Blind Stitched)
Wind Mesh back panel
YKK Front-zip
Aquabarrier
Back knee emboss
Hex-tech kneepads
Velcro ankle closure straps (included)
Non slip cuffs
Heat sealed cuff edges
Key pocket 2.0: keyloop with mini buckle
Aquaflush 2.0
MATERIALS:
MX4 Yamamoto neoprene
Flaremesh+ in chest and back
Fox Fleece in lower body
TECHNOLOGY:
Waterproof stretch taping critical areas - A highly durable taping is used in the crucial areas of the suit to avoid leaking and keep it flexible and warm.
Glued blind stitching is a method whereby the panels are first glued together and then only stitched halfway through the fabric instead of fully perforating it, which makes the seams waterproof.
Wind mesh has closed cell neoprene with one side of fabric lamination. The outside of the mesh neoprene offers a better protection against wind chill.
Aquabarrier - This is a silicone printing on the collarbone region of your wetsuit. This forms a barrier between the overlapping front-zip panels preventing water from entering.
Key pocket 2.0 - A key loop with mini buckle - An external neoprene key pocket conveniently positioned on the lower leg of the suit. The standard key loop is now equipped with a mini-buckle to release your key with ease while making sure your key is safe inside.
Aquabarrier - This is a silicone printing on the collarbone region of your wetsuit. This forms a barrier between the overlapping front-zip panels preventing water from entering.

name: Womens Furno 3/2mm GBS Back Zip Wetsuit
description:
Get a FREE Nyord hanger when you buy a Nyord wetsuit. Produced in the UK using 100% recycled ocean plastics.

Perfect for you if: You’re a summer surfer who surfs occasionally, or you’re new to surfing.

Balancing excellent value and quality, Nyord's entry-price wetsuit incorporates some high-end features at an affordable price. Made with the same super-stretchy limestone neoprene as our more expensive wetsuits, combined with a fast-dry jersey lining so you can get back on the water faster. Glued and blind stitched seams, as well as taping on key areas of wear, provide a watertight and durable seal. Anti-slip ankle and wrist cuffs prevent water from flushing your suit. 

THE DETAILS:
Super-stretch Limestone Neoprene - Derived from limestone, Nyord's super-stretch neoprene delivers great flexibility and reduces our reliance on oil by replacing traditional petroleum-based neoprene.
GBS Seams - Panel edges are glued together and stitched on the inside. The neoprene is only partially perforated, resulting in a watertight and flexible seam.
Glideskin Neck - Glideskin is a very stretchy and comfortable type of neoprene. It sits snugly against the skin to prevent flushing.
Anti-slip Ankle & Wrist Cuffs - Anti-slip cuffs stay put for a more comfortable fit and create a watertight seal to prevent flushing.

name: Womens ReWired 3/2mm GBS Chest Zip Wetsuit
description:
The best-selling ReWired now features Halo X2 neoprene throughout the upper body. This new neoprene is made from waste scrap car tyres, oyster shells and plastic bottles, and without solvent-based glues or chemical yarn dying. The new ReWired is a huge leap forward in our journey towards sustainability, with zero loss in performance. With new under-the-hood enhancements in stretch through the body and legs, the ReWired feels better than ever in the water. The ultimate high performance wetsuit. Featuring Rip Curl’s latest E6 neoprene with Thermo Lining throughout the entire suit, combined with our newest zip free entry system for maximum paddling freedom and water seal.

E6 NEOPRENE
Premium high stretch, lightweight neoprene 30% more stretch and 20% lighter than E4.
E6 TAPE

Benchmark stretch for unrestricted performance.
E6 THERMO LINING

Super high stretch performance lining that surpasses industry  standards.  25% more stretch  than E5.
E6 STRESS POINT HAND TAPE
Ultimate stretch tape with Flash Lining for ultimate, stretch, warmth and comfort.
ZIP FREE ENTRY
Zip Free technology offers light, unrestricted performance and efficient design for maximum stretch, warmth, and comfort.

name: Womens E-Bomb LTD 3/2mm Zip Free Wetsuit
description:
The E7 Limited Edition E-Bomb is the result of a 3 year project with World Champions Tyler Wright, Mick Fanning, Gabriel Medina and the Rip Curl Wetsuit team.

Featuring Rip Curl’s latest high stretch ‘E7’ neoprene in the upper body, the Limited Edition E-Bomb has been designed with a unique ‘one piece’ upper body panel without seams that stretches from wrist to wrist and provides the Ultimate stretch performance of ‘E7’.

The body of the Limited Edition E-Bomb has E6 neoprene with internal thermo lining for stretch, warmth and comfort.

NEW E7 Neoprene upper body - Unique ‘one piece’ upper body panel without seams that stretches from wrist to wrist and provides the Ultimate stretch performance of ‘E7’

E6 Neoprene lower body - Premium high stretch, lightweight neoprene 30% more stretch and 20% lighter than E4.
E6 Stress point hand tape - Ultimate stretch tape with Flash Lining for ultimate, stretch, warmth and comfort.
E6 Thermo lining on body - Super high stretch performance lining that surpasses industry standards. 25% more stretch than E5.
E6 Tape - Benchmark stretch for unrestricted performance.
Zip Free Entry - Zip Free technology offers light, unrestricted performance and efficient design for maximum stretch, warmth, and comfort.
New underarm torpedo gusset panel provides increased comfort and improved fit.
All new pattern designed by world champions for their performance needs
Over 3 years of extensive research and development alongside Rip Curl world champion surfers Gabriel Medina, Tyler Wright and Mick Fanning.

name: Womens Omega 3/2mm GBS Back Zip Wetsuit
description:
The Omega incorporates some high-end features including E5 Neoprene and E3 Neoprene at an economical price.

HYDRO LOC COLLAR
Neoprene neck collar designed to minimise leakage and effectively hold up batwing.
SEALED GBS
Triple glued, double stitched seam does not fully penetrate neopren allowing for a high stretch, high strengthm water sealed seam.
3/4 E3 NEOPRENE
Standard high stretch, lightweight neoprene with high durability properties.
E5 NEOPRENE
Premium high stretch, lightweight neoprene with 30% more stretch, 20% less weight, and 10 more warmth compared to E4.
MESH SKIN PANELS
Smooth mesh panels that absorb solar heat and reduce wind chill.
E5 STRESS POINT TAPED
Increased durability through taping of critical neoprene panel junctions.

name: Womens Furnace 3/2mm Chest Zip Wetsuit
description:
Boost your heat and your airs with the Women's Furnace Comp Series Chest Zip Full Wetsuit. Delivering on sustainability without sacrifice, this cold-water competition performance wetsuit for women is now made with innovative eco-conscious materials. Geared for competition, the cold water full wetsuit is lined at the front and back panels with incredibly lightweight and strong Graphene-infused yarns, now infused with 100% recycled fibers, keeping you warmer and faster for longer. Made from upcycled car tires, the eco-conscious SMART Foam is topped with AIRLITE Recycler jersey, now made from recycled materials, radically reducing both weight and wind chill. A chest zip entry system allows for an easy on-off. Every layer is constructed with incredible flexibility for optimal performance.

Women's Furnace Comp Series Full Wetsuit.
Exterior Fabric Type: AIRLITE 4D Recycler with 20% more stretch.
Neoprene Foam Type: SMART Foam - partially recycled, Premium light weight.
Interior Fabric Type: Graphene Recycler Plus combined with Airlite Graphene.
Body type: Long Sleeve Full suit.
Entry System: Chest Zip.
Internal Seam Detail: Machine Applied Super-flex neo tape.

name: Womens Synergy 3/2mm Back Zip GBS Wetsuit
description:
The Synergy Series wetsuits deliver lightweight, premium heat, and innovative technology with superior value and durability. Made from stretchy and eco-conscious Superlight neoprene combined with glued and blind stitched sealed external seams, the women’s Synergy Back Zip Full Wetsuit boasts excellent thermal retention. Graphene recycler lining at the front and back panels adds incredible strength and heat without adding bulk, while silicone stretch panels at the arms and legs let you get in and out with ease. Finished with a back zip entry, the Synergy delivers everything you demand from a premium wetsuit, without breaking the bank.

Women's Synergy Full Wetsuit.

Interior Fabric Type: Graphene Recycler Plus combined with Silicon Stretch.
